#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.combine.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.combine"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:1 of
msgid "Combine the Series with a Series or scalar according to `func`."
msgstr "根据 `func` 将 Series 与另一个 Series 或标量进行合并。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:3 of
msgid ""
"Combine the Series and `other` using `func` to perform elementwise "
"selection for combined Series. `fill_value` is assumed when value is "
"missing at some index from one of the two objects being combined."
msgstr ""
"使用 `func` 对 Series 和 `other` 进行元素级操作以生成合并后的 Series。当"
"两个对象中某一个在某个索引处缺失值时，使用 `fill_value` 填充。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:8 of
msgid "The value(s) to be combined with the `Series`."
msgstr "要与 `Series` 合并的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:10 of
msgid "Function that takes two scalars as inputs and returns an element."
msgstr "接受两个标量作为输入并返回一个元素的函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:12 of
msgid ""
"The value to assume when an index is missing from one Series or the "
"other. The default specifies to use the appropriate NaN value for the "
"underlying dtype of the Series."
msgstr ""
"当某个索引在一个 Series 中缺失时所使用的默认值。默认值会根据 Series 的"
"底层数据类型使用相应的 NaN 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:17 of
msgid "The result of combining the Series with the other object."
msgstr "将 Series 与其他对象合并后的结果。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.combine_first`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:23 of
msgid "Combine Series values, choosing the calling Series' values first."
msgstr "合并 Series 的值，优先选择调用 Series 的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:26 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:27 of
msgid ""
"Consider 2 Datasets ``s1`` and ``s2`` containing highest clocked speeds "
"of different birds."
msgstr "考虑两个数据集 ``s1`` 和 ``s2``，它们包含不同鸟类的最高速度。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:43 of
msgid ""
"Now, to combine the two datasets and view the highest speeds of the birds"
" across the two datasets"
msgstr "现在，合并这两个数据集，并查看所有鸟类在这两个数据集中记录的最高速度"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.combine.series_combine:52 of
msgid ""
"In the previous example, the resulting value for duck is missing, because"
" the maximum of a NaN and a float is a NaN. So, in the example, we set "
"``fill_value=0``, so the maximum value returned will be the value from "
"some dataset."
msgstr ""
"在前面的例子中，由于 NaN 与浮点数的最大值仍然是 NaN，因此鸭子（duck）的"
"结果值缺失。所以在示例中我们设置了 ``fill_value=0``，这样返回的最大值将会"
"是某个数据集中的实际值。"

